{"lemma":"خَرِب","slug":"خَرِب","root":"خ.ر.ب","root_slug":"خ-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10233","","n10238","n10239","n10240","n10241"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to demolish, devastate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pierce, bore (especially the ears)"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"ruined, wrecked, destroyed","examples":[{"text":"The sun was sinking down over the sea, the mountain wall with all its clefts and promontories wore a cloak of many colours, when we saw before us on a rock a ruined tower.","english":"The Tragedy"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic. Compare Aramaic חֲרוֹב (“be laid waste”), Classical Syriac ܚܪܒ (“be laid waste”), Hebrew חָרַב (kharáv, “to be destroyed”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10233","headword_ar":"خَرِبَ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, A, Msb, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, S, * A, Mgh, * Msb, KL, TA,) said of a place, (S,) or a country, (A, Mgh, *) or a dwelling, or place of abode, (Msb,) or a house, (TK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of ruin, waste, uninhabited, depopulated, deserted, desolate, uncultivated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state the contrary of flourishing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, A, Mgh, KL, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EimaArapN","text_ar":"عِمَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xariba","text_ar":"خَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabN","text_ar":"خَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It had in it a slit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a round perforation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had his ear slit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bored with a round perforation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraba","text_ar":"خَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4. ―         -b2-  Also, (Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiraAbapN","text_ar":"خِرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stole:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became a thief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"robber."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraba A_ibila fulaAnK","text_ar":"خَرَبَ اـِبِلَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, *) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraba biA_ibili fulaAnK","text_ar":"خَرَبَ بِاـِبِلِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) both mentioned as on the authority of Lh, (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiraAbapN","text_ar":"خِرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbapN","text_ar":"خَرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuruwbN","text_ar":"خُرُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stole the camels of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabahu","text_ar":"خَرَبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bored it, perforated it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a hole through it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he slit it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) namely, a thing. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the part where the head of his thigh-bone was inserted;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrbp","text_ar":"خربة"},{"kind":"text","text":"here has some other of the significations assigned to it in this article. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["JK","K","S","Msb","TK","A","Mgh","KL","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n10238","headword_ar":"خَرْبٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabN","text_ar":"خَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10239","headword_ar":"خُرْبٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in seven places.       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place where an elevated accumulation of sand terminates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, S, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"producing trees of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaDFA","text_ar":"غَضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10240","headword_ar":"خَرَبٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of bustard called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubaAraY","text_ar":"حُبَارَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubaAraY","text_ar":"حُبَارَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", absolutely: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xirobaAnN","text_ar":"خِرْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (A,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaribN","text_ar":"خَرِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarobN","text_ar":"خَرْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xirib~aAnN","text_ar":"خِرِبَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cowardly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a coward."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xurobapN","text_ar":"خُرْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end of the paragraph."}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","A","JK"]},{"entry_id":"n10241","headword_ar":"خَرِبٌ","root":"xrb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In a state of ruin, waste, uninhabited, depopulated, deserted, desolate, uncultivated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state the contrary of flourishing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, TA;) applied to a place, (S,) or a country, (A,) or a dwelling, or place of abode. (Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daArN xaribapN","text_ar":"دَارٌ خَرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A house which its owner has reduced to ruin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered uninhabited,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (S, TA.) [In the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA juHoru","text_ar":"هٰذَا جُحْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~K xaribK","text_ar":"ضَبٍّ خَرِبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is a deserted hole of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"lizard of the kind called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dabb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the word"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xrb","text_ar":"خرب"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the gen. case"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AljiwaAri","text_ar":"عَلَى الجِوَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. because of its proximity to a preceding word in that case, not being so properly.] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa xaribu AlEaZomi","text_ar":"هُوَ خَرِبُ العَظْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is without marrow in the bone"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaribu AlA^amaAnapi","text_ar":"خَرِبُ الاَمَانَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in whom trust is not safely reposed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAbN","text_ar":"خَرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarabN","text_ar":"خَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","TA","A","Msb"]}]}}